Lectura de la base de datos.

cel_1 <- read.csv("celular1.csv")
cel_2 <- read.csv("celular2.csv")
cel_3 <- read.csv("celular3.csv")

Llevar la base de datos a cada segundo (celular1)

cel_1_x_seg <- cel_1 %>%
              mutate(timestamp_seg = trunc(timestamp/1000)) %>%
              group_by(timestamp_seg) %>%
              summarise(DecibelProm1 = mean(DecibelSource, na.rm = TRUE),
                        n = n(), 
                        na = sum(is.na(DecibelSource)))
summary(cel_1_x_seg)
##  timestamp_seg        DecibelProm1         n              na   
##  Min.   :1.519e+09   Min.   :19.31   Min.   : 4.0   Min.   :0  
##  1st Qu.:1.519e+09   1st Qu.:27.23   1st Qu.:24.0   1st Qu.:0

Unir las dos bases de datos por tiempo

library(dplyr)

cel_1_2 <- cel_1_x_seg %>%
           select(timestamp_seg, DecibelProm1) %>%
           inner_join(select(cel_2_x_seg, timestamp_seg, DecibelProm2), 
                      by = "timestamp_seg")
cel_1_2_3 <- cel_1_2 %>%
             inner_join(select(cel_3_x_seg, timestamp_seg, DecibelProm3),
                        by = "timestamp_seg")
summary(cel_1_2_3)
##  timestamp_seg        DecibelProm1    DecibelProm2    DecibelProm3  
##  Min.   :1.519e+09   Min.   :19.31   Min.   :37.07   Min.   :18.19  
##  1st Qu.:1.519e+09   1st Qu.:27.17   1st Qu.:44.02   1st Qu.:26.32  
##  Median :1.519e+09   Median :33.93   Median :51.72   Median :33.63  
##  Mean   :1.519e+09   Mean   :33.46   Mean   :50.92   Mean   :32.95  
##  3rd Qu.:1.519e+09   3rd Qu.:39.52   3rd Qu.:57.21   3rd Qu.:39.29  
##  Max.   :1.519e+09   Max.   :53.41   Max.   :69.37   Max.   :50.73

Creación de la variable fecha

library(dplyr)
cel_1_2_3 <- cel_1_2_3 %>%
             mutate(fecha = as.POSIXct(timestamp_seg, origin="1970-01-01"))
summary(cel_1_2_3)
##  timestamp_seg        DecibelProm1    DecibelProm2    DecibelProm3       fecha                    
##  Min.   :1.519e+09   Min.   :19.31   Min.   :37.07   Min.   :18.19   Min.   :2018-02-16 06:44:10  
##  1st Qu.:1.519e+09   1st Qu.:27.17   1st Qu.:44.02   1st Qu.:26.32   1st Qu.:2018-02-16 06:55:33  
##  Median :1.519e+09   Median :33.93   Median :51.72   Median :33.63   Median :2018-02-16 07:06:56  
##  Mean   :1.519e+09   Mean   :33.46   Mean   :50.92   Mean   :32.95   Mean   :2018-02-16 07:06:56  
##  3rd Qu.:1.519e+09   3rd Qu.:39.52   3rd Qu.:57.21   3rd Qu.:39.29   3rd Qu.:2018-02-16 07:18:19  
##  Max.   :1.519e+09   Max.   :53.41   Max.   :69.37   Max.   :50.73   Max.   :2018-02-16 07:29:42

Transformarlo a formato largo

library(tidyr)
cel_1_2_3_long <- cel_1_2_3 %>%
   gather(key = celular, value = Decibel, -c(timestamp_seg, fecha))

Graficación

library(ggplot2)
ggplot(cel_1_2_3_long, aes(fecha, Decibel, col = celular)) +
  geom_line(alpha = 0.5) 

library(ggplot2)
ggplot(cel_1_2_3_long, aes(fecha, Decibel, col = celular)) +
  geom_line(alpha = 0.5) +
  facet_grid(celular ~ .)

library(ggplot2)
ggplot(cel_1_2_3_long, aes(celular, Decibel)) +
  geom_boxplot()

library(ggplot2)
ggplot(cel_1_2_3_long, aes(celular, Decibel)) +
  geom_violin()

pairs(cel_1_2_3[, -c(1, 5)])
